{"tid":887820,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"我張卡無啦啦話要格式化才能使用","createTime":"2018-11-03T08:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T23:42:26.000Z","uid":167326,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f200d109c3e09ece20e9ff5e83962643149db446","tid":887820,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T08:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1tU8BW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1tU8BW.png&h=a81d634f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kBgfS4x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkBgfS4x.png&h=8cf7d3ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我拍完啲片 諗住過落電腦<br />\n點知過到一半 佢無啦啦跳左 <br />\n然後就話要格式化先可以用 <br />\n<br />\n死啦 格式化左會唔會乜都冇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解決好"},{"pid":"cc5a7b8e8f19a71dc4146800b23338555a198f9b","tid":887820,"uid":43493,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T08:38:28.000Z","msg":"入嚟食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f79b1426a88393a35d74f5247b6585ad52c045","tid":887820,"uid":167326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc5a7b8e8f19a71dc4146800b23338555a198f9b","tid":887820,"uid":43493,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T08:38:28.000Z","msg":"入嚟食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T08:59:15.000Z","msg":"好撚唔開心呀 最近真係運氣差到貼地 唉<br />\n會唔會拎去保養之類有得整番"},{"pid":"746a5639bec801a06b1f4807fd23f0d2637bd8cd","tid":887820,"uid":9941,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T09:02:44.000Z","msg":"Sandisk合理<br />\n無得救<br />\nBlacklist 左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6f6597a9b3e84fd46fe1b402e0b7fdce0c71e58","tid